penrose.dsl:
type Symbol -- an element of a sequence type Sequence -- a sequence of symbols
type Cell -- an element of a matrix predicate Value(Cell c, String w) -- set a cell value predicate Color(Cell c, Number r, Number g, Number b) -- set a cell color
type Matrix -- a 2D array of cells predicate Dim(Matrix M, Number m, Number n) -- set matrix size to mxn predicate Elem(Cell c, Matrix M, Number i, Number j) -- add cell to matrix at (i,j)
-- set row and col labels predicate RowLabel(Matrix M, Number i, String l) predicate ColLabel(Matrix M, Number j, String l)
type Arrow -- arrows lead link a cell to another predicate highlight(Arrow q) -- highlight an arrow
constructor Step(Cell q, Cell r) -> Arrow -- straight arrow between cells constructor Arc(Cell q, Cell r) -> Arrow -- curved arrow between cells
